{"tid":1792040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有大頭]警屯門截查《立場新聞》記者　強搶手機阻拍攝　扯爛記者設備袋","createTime":"2019-12-21T10:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T11:28:32.000Z","uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d2af9b207e0c702226c77b0c7e2621a99ce7b020","tid":1792040,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T10:11:18.000Z","msg":"《立場新聞》記者今天到屯門公園採訪候任區議員記者會前，在入口天后橋外遭五、六名防暴警員截查，期間被喝停拍攝、強搶手機。<br />\n<br />\n時為下午二時四十五分，記者在屯門天后路天后橋一休憩公園準備採訪。在進入屯門公園採訪候任區議員記者會前，突然有五、六名防暴警員落車趨前截查。記者被喝令「咪走」、「企喺度」，又著記者停止拍攝，記者查詢停機原因，未得結果，隨即被搶去拍攝中的手機。<br />\n<br />\n截查期間，記者用來裝置設備的隨行布袋被警員扯爛。警員著記者把背包的物品拿岀來，也要求記者關手機。查完記者的記者証與身份証後，告誡記者被截查時「要企定」「唔好捉雞仔咁四圍走」，又指「而家唔係你（記者）話事」，「叫你唔好影就唔好影」。<br />\n<br />\n防暴警問記者收到甚麼消息，待會屯門公園一帶會有甚麼事情發生，又追問携帶頭盔護具的因由，又稱正常採訪不用帶這些東西。<br />\n<br />\n警員不停重申，記者被截查應立即合作，「叫你停機就停機，而家係你被截查。」記者被查問約十分鐘後執拾個人物品離開，前往屯門公園採訪「屯門公園大媽」噪音問題候任區議員記者會，惟因隨行袋孭帶被破壞，整天的採訪與移動效率將受影響。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》強烈譴責警方一再施暴阻撓記者拍攝採訪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E6%88%AA%E6%9F%A5-%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85-%E5%BC%B7%E6%90%B6%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E9%98%BB%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D-%E6%89%AF%E7%88%9B%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99%E8%A2%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%2588%25AA%25E6%259F%25A5-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585-%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E6%2590%25B6%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%2598%25BB%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%2594%259D-%25E6%2589%25AF%25E7%2588%259B%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E5%2582%2599%25E8%25A2%258B%2F&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3ADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=3de73882\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%2588%25AA%25E6%259F%25A5-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585-%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E6%2590%25B6%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%2598%25BB%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%2594%259D-%25E6%2589%25AF%25E7%2588%259B%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E5%2582%2599%25E8%25A2%258B%2F&h=6996886b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E6%88%AA%E6%9F%A5-%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85-%E5%BC%B7%E6%90%B6%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E9%98%BB%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D-%E6%89%AF%E7%88%9B%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99%E8%A2%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Screenshot202019-12-2120at205.40.3020PM20copy_JvNca_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FScreenshot202019-12-2120at205.40.3020PM20copy_JvNca_1200x0.png&h=7318e0a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/80055864_10159093612423998_5868639898755399680_o20copy_7c8wH_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F80055864_10159093612423998_5868639898755399680_o20copy_7c8wH_1200x0.png&h=b6ae386f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c49c33b3ea89217d29e7004cee1eeac5a3af9779","tid":1792040,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T10:11:44.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推得唔得，重要行動post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxdmjGx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxdmjGx.png&h=69ee17c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［主線任務］聽日1530嘅維吾爾族集會獲不反對通知書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1791988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1791988</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d810688e91a8096b59dd27e5859d4bfa0818e949","tid":1792040,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T10: